{"tid":1511466,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"應否設立popo專用篤灰平台？","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T14:17:03.000Z","uid":276716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c24e88410f19c5b5f4e1c8bf1dd63fe54b7cebb","tid":1511466,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"睇到一篇報導<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">近年警察不敢在警局內隨便打人，因為除了搜身房，很多地方皆有閉路電視。我問：「有閉路電視又點？警察唔係互相包庇咩？」朋友的答案有點出人意表：所謂「日防夜防，阿頭難防」，警隊內有些上司，其實很落力捉下屬的違規行為，藉此獲得上級嘉獎，增加升職機會，所以下面那群警員，都懂得自保之道。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190821/20752635\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F20752635&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxnbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=cdf04f9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190821%2F20752635&h=591c796f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/馮睎乾/daily/article/20190821/20752635</a><br />\n<br />\n既然popo係會篤灰，點解唔設立一個渠道，畀佢地安全地篤灰？<br />\n有人嘅地方就有是非。爭上位，口和心不口，小圈子拉幫結派，popo都一定有啦。<br />\n虐老單case都顯示咗高層係唔介犧牲啲散仔，輕則革職，重則告上法庭。<br />\n咁如果畀popo用匿名方式篤灰，例如開個篤灰TG，鼓勵佢地互篤。至於收到嘅料係真係假，都唔需要深究，因為只要令popo內部有猜忌就足夠。到時上司驚畀下屬篤，team A 驚畀 Team B篤，咁點做嘢？<br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗呢？"},{"pid":"dae7366d418f418d5dfdc092ba74390fd3e3c246","tid":1511466,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"[置頂-連登改變世界]929全球集會抗赤納粹，召喚攬炒巴，G20巴，動畫巴，各文宣巴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港人入黎幫手，成敗一戰，只需大家一步"},{"pid":"2e4c1418b729e23426ded488b722f8df349af0d9","tid":1511466,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"有老豆揾仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1cebf3d84eb18fc33a41a4c7ee845cbc639e763","tid":1511466,"uid":197424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"經過呢三個月仲會係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adf320b3fca6467f82c5e3a9b10fbcb3eac5855","tid":1511466,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"打狗台"}]}